beer.beer_description: Brewed and barrel aged to celebrate our 2nd Anniversary. Aged 350 days in French oak Chardonnay barrels gives this beer a spicy white wine oaky character. We then added fresh raspberry puree for a different flavor profile and point of difference from the standalone barrel aged offering. Very dry base beer with added fruity body super easy to drink and refreshing.
